<HEADLINE> Shanghai Mayor Meets Tung Chee Hwa </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, June 2 (Xinhua) -- Shanghai Mayor Xu Kuangdi met
today with Chief Executive Tung Chee Hwa of the Hong Kong Special
Administrative Region (SAR), who is here attending a seminar on
the metropolis development.
</P>
<P>
Xu briefed Tung Chee Hwa on Shanghai's rapid economic growth
and the development of the Pudong New Area in the city.
</P>
<P>
Tung Chee Hwa, who is on his third visit to Shanghai since he
assumed the office, said he hopes that the two metropolises will
promote cooperation in economic, high-tech and financial areas,
and they will achieve an even greater development in the new
century.
</P>
<P>
Tung Chee Hwa addressed the opening ceremony of the seminar and
visited the Shanghai Stock Exchange earlier today. 
