million U.S. dollars) in the past four years for young and
returned scientists to do scientific and technological research.
The fund has helped more than 40 scientific developments go into
production.
</P>
<P>
The city will invest 200 million yuan (24 million U.S. dollars)
before 2002 to help higher learning institutions establish
scientific and technological zones and high-tech incubation bases.
