Canadian dollars (about 9.89 U.S. dollars) at 146.75 Canadian
dollars (about 98.06 U.S. dollars), Certicom Corp., up 14.55 (
about 9.72 U.S. dollars) at 62 (about 41.43 U.S. dollars) and 724
Solutions Inc., up 12.50 (about 8.35 U.S. dollars) at 66 Canadian
dollars (about 44.10 U.S. dollars). (Canada-Stock)
