<HEADLINE> New Website Offers Online Medical Service </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
FUZHOU, June 2 (Xinhua) -- A newly-launched website has made it
possible for patients to seek expert treatment via the Internet.
</P>
<P>
By accessing the website at WWW.TCM-HOTLINE.COM, patients may
have their symptoms diagnosed by an automatic diagnosis system,
which will not only suggest treatment options but also recommend
hospitals and medical experts to the patients.
</P>
<P>
The new website, jointly launched by two Internet ventures in
Fuzhou and Hong Kong, also features a database on traditional
Chinese medicine, providing detailed information and knowledge
about the medical science, herbal medicine, medical appliances,
and related educational institutions.
</P>
<P>
Special care service is also available at the website,
providing health care knowledge concerning the elderly, expectant
mothers, the sick and babies. 
